==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Metallochrome
<hw>Me*tal"lo*chrome</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Metallochromy</er>.]</ety> <def>A coloring produced by the
deposition of some metallic compound; specifically, the prismatic tints
produced by depositing a film of peroxide of lead on polished steel by
electricity.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Metallochromy</ent>⟦br⟧
